-against- : 19 Cr. 830(AT)

Upon the letter application of Jason E. Foy, Esq, attorney for the defendant, TOVA NOEL, for an Order mandating the release of the firearm and all other property surrendered the New York City Police Department as a condition of bail back to the defendant,
